Usage: getWhatIfTimingMode [-help] [-context] [-defaultOutputCap] [-model]
                           [-portPriority] [-quiet] [-nonDefault]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-context                               # Mode Description
                                       # (enums={in out}, default=out)
-defaultOutputCap                      # Default Output Capacitance
                                       # (float, default=0)
-model                                 # Model
                                       # (enums={intrinsic normalized}, default=normalized)
-portPriority                          # Port Priority
                                       # (enums={cellType portParam}, default=portParam)
-quiet                                 # Displays the current settings in Tcl list format only
-nonDefault                            # Displays the current settings which are not default settings